Dialogue: 2,0:00:00.15,0:00:01.55,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,盗版电影
Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.15,0:00:01.55,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Bootleg copies of movies. 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:01.55,0:00:05.39,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,就是那种“你总不会去偷车吧”之类的公益广告里天天警告我们的玩意儿
Dialogue: 1,0:00:01.55,0:00:05.39,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,The ones they warned us about from, like, you wouldn't download a piracy or whatever.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:05.39,0:00:10.82,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,基本上就是电影的非官方发行版，而且我先声明啊，我本人可不搞盗版
Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.39,0:00:10.82,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,These are essentially unofficially released versions of films and, full disclosure, I don't pirate anything.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:10.82,0:00:12.80,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,我这么说可不是为了讨好B站申鹤
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.82,0:00:12.80,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And I'm not just saying that for YouTube's sake. 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:12.80,0:00:16.68,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,我是真不怎么看电视，反正我想看的东西总有正规渠道
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.80,0:00:16.68,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,I mean, I don't really watch actual TV and I can only access the stuff I want to watch anyway.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:16.68,0:00:18.37,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而且我现在基本只看B站
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.68,0:00:18.37,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And still, I only really watch YouTube, 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:18.37,0:00:22.61,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这玩意儿本来就是免费的，但我还是想聊聊盗版电影这东西
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.37,0:00:22.61,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,which is free anyway. But I still want to take a look at bootleg copies of movies.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.61,0:00:24.32,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,尤其是盗版DVD
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.61,0:00:24.32,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Specifically, bootleg DVDs, 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:24.32,0:00:26.55,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,多亏了互联网，这玩意儿现在基本已经凉透了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.32,0:00:26.55,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,which are pretty much dead thanks to the internet 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:26.55,0:00:28.64,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,因为盗版DVD你好歹还得花钱买
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.55,0:00:28.64,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,because you'd still have to pay for a bootleg DVD,
Dialogue: 2,0:00:28.64,0:00:30.48,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,只是比正版便宜很多而已
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.64,0:00:30.48,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,just a lot less than a normal DVD. 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:30.48,0:00:34.64,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但只要你在网上那些犄角旮旯里逛逛，你甚至一分钱都不用花
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.48,0:00:34.64,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But just by looking around sketchy parts of the internet, you won't have to pay.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:34.64,0:00:37.46,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,然后顺便给电脑安上五十个该死的病毒
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.64,0:00:37.46,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And you'll also install 50 fucking viruses. 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:37.46,0:00:39.94,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,话说回来，我手里还真有几张这种盘
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.46,0:00:39.94,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Now, I own a couple of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.46,0:00:39.94,Yahei-1920x1080,atg3,0,0,0,,怎么没有古迦奥特曼
Dialogue: 2,0:00:39.94,0:00:44.38,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,澄清一下，我可不是什么律师，我就是个做卡通视频的油管博主
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.94,0:00:44.38,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Now, to clarify, I'm no lawyer who could have guessed I make YouTube videos about cartoons and stuff.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:44.38,0:00:48.34,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但我觉得我持有这些玩意儿，严格来说应该不算犯法吧，毕竟，我也是受害者啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.38,0:00:48.34,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But I don't think it's technically illegal for me to own these. I mean, I'm a victim here.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:48.34,0:00:51.97,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,当初我买这些盘的时候，商家可是当正品卖给我的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.34,0:00:51.97,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,When I bought all these, I was sold them as if they were perfectly real.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:51.97,0:00:55.96,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,我哪知道这是假的，你看这包装，简直天衣无缝嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.97,0:00:55.96,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,How was I supposed to know this is fake? Looks perfectly legitimate to me.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:55.96,0:00:57.40,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,不过我是不能卖这些盘的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.96,0:00:57.40,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,I can't sell these though, 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:57.40,0:01:01.11,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,因为那就成了销售盗版产品了，所以这些玩意儿就只能砸我手里了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.40,0:01:01.11,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,because then I'm selling a bootleg product, so I'm stuck with these now.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:01.11,0:01:05.48,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,行了，我们来看看盗版拷贝的种类，先从“枪版”说起
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.11,0:01:05.48,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Anyway, now on to the types of pirate copies, starting with cam copies.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:05.48,0:01:09.36,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,想干嘛就干嘛，因为海盗是自由的，你就是个海盗！
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.48,0:01:09.36,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Do what you want because a pirate is free! You are a pirate!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:09.36,0:01:11.25,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这玩意儿可以说是最“非官方”的版本了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.36,0:01:11.25,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,These are about as unofficial as they get. 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:11.25,0:01:13.77,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,枪版的基本操作就是，一个哥们儿或者姐们儿
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.25,0:01:13.77,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,The basic concept of a camera if he's a guy or girl,
Dialogue: 2,0:01:13.77,0:01:17.95,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,犯罪不分性别嘛，溜进电影院，再偷带一个破摄像机
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.77,0:01:17.95,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,which is a gender-neutral crime, goes into a movie theatre and sneaks in a shitty camcorder,
Dialogue: 2,0:01:17.95,0:01:19.85,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,然后想办法藏起来，按下录制键
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.95,0:01:19.85,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,then hides it somehow and hits record. 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:19.85,0:01:22.02,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,搞定，他现在就有了一份属于自己的《鲨鱼黑帮》拷贝了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.85,0:01:22.02,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Boom! Now he has his very own copy of Shark Tale.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:22.02,0:01:25.82,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但要说这玩意儿是看电影的好方式，那绝对是扯淡
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.02,0:01:25.82,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Now, while these are all a good way to watch a movie, fucking no.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:25.82,0:01:28.38,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,不过说实话，这玩意儿还真有种别样的魅力
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.82,0:01:28.38,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But, I can't lie, there is sort of a charm to these.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:28.38,0:01:32.96,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,你能听到观众的现场反应，体验到一种你可能从未在影院感受过的氛围
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.38,0:01:32.96,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,You get to hear the audience reactions to a movie you might have never been able to experience in theatres.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:32.96,0:01:36.46,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,或者见证人们第一次看到那些如今已是名场面时的反应
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.96,0:01:36.46,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Or witness people's first reactions to now famous movie scenes.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:36.46,0:01:40.44,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,更别提那种背德感了，天呐，这家伙随时都可能被抓包
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.46,0:01:40.44,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Not to mention the thrill of knowing, ooh, this guy could be caught at any moment.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:40.44,0:01:42.55,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而当他真的被抓时……
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.44,0:01:42.55,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And when it does happen...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:50.74,0:01:51.56,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,顶级智斗
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.74,0:01:51.56,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Breathtaking.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:51.56,0:01:54.46,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,我记得我只有两次看枪版的经历
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.56,0:01:54.46,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Now, I only had two experiences I can remember with cam copies.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:54.46,0:01:56.94,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,那是我在土耳其之类的地方度假的时候
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.46,0:01:56.94,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And that's when I was on vacation somewhere like Turkey.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:56.94,0:01:58.10,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,我也不确定是不是土耳其
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.94,0:01:58.10,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,I don't know if it was Turkey.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:58.10,0:01:59.40,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但反正是个类似的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.10,0:01:59.40,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But it was somewhere like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:59.40,0:02:02.16,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,当时有小贩在卖还没上映的电影DVD
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.40,0:02:02.16,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And there was guys selling DVDs of movies that weren't out yet.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:02.16,0:02:02.94,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,我的天呐
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.16,0:02:02.94,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Oh my god!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:02.94,0:02:03.88,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,太带派了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.94,0:02:03.88,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,This is crazy!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:03.88,0:02:06.00,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,我当时还以为这些电影在我们那儿已经出DVD了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.88,0:02:06.00,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,These movies must have already come out on DVD here.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:06.00,0:02:09.60,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,于是我买了2016版的《超能敢死队》和《冰川时代5：星际碰撞》
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.00,0:02:09.60,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,So I bought Ghostbusters 2016 and Ice Age Collision Course.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:09.60,0:02:12.94,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,结果都是些画质烂到没法看的枪版
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.60,0:02:12.94,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And they were shitty cam copies that were unwatchable.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:12.94,0:02:15.24,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,我现在已经没留着了，你说我留着那玩意儿干嘛呢
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.94,0:02:15.24,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,I don't have them anymore because why would I keep them?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:15.24,0:02:18.41,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,不过它们都装在这样的套子里，看起来大概是这个样子
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.24,0:02:18.41,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But they came in a sleeve like this and sort of looked like this.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:18.41,0:02:21.14,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,是啊，用这种方式看电影体验很差，但是……
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.41,0:02:21.14,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Yeah, this isn't a good way to experience these movies, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:21.14,0:02:23.22,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这两部电影真的有好的欣赏方式吗
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.14,0:02:23.22,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Is there even a good way to experience these movies?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:23.22,0:02:23.83,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,大概没有吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.22,0:02:23.83,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:23.83,0:02:25.88,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,那么，这些人是怎么被抓到的呢
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.83,0:02:25.88,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Now, how do these people get caught?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:25.88,0:02:29.12,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,嗯，一些电影院开始给员工发奖金
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.88,0:02:29.12,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Well, some movie theatres have begun offering rewards to employees
Dialogue: 2,0:02:29.12,0:02:31.46,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,只要他们能抓住录制电影的人就给钱
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.12,0:02:31.46,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,who are able to catch people recording movies.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.06,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,比如一千英镑
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.06,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Things like £1000, 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:33.06,0:02:35.26,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这很可能会让更多偷录的人被抓
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.06,0:02:35.26,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,which is likely going to increase the amount of people caught
Dialogue: 2,0:02:35.26,0:02:37.70,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,从电影院的角度来看这很合理
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.26,0:02:37.70,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,and make sense from a movie theatre's perspective.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:37.70,0:02:40.62,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,如果网上有免费的电影可以看，他们还怎么卖票呢
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.70,0:02:40.62,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,If there's a free version of the movie they're charging you to see online,
Dialogue: 2,0:02:40.62,0:02:42.27,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,谁还会花钱去看呢
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.62,0:02:42.27,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,why would people pay to see it?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:42.27,0:02:43.58,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,所以他们会损失一大笔钱
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.27,0:02:43.58,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,So they'll lose a lot of money.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:43.58,0:02:47.33,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,因此花一小笔钱来阻止这种行为是完全说得通的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.58,0:02:47.33,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,So spending a tiny bit of money in comparison to try and stop it makes sense.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:47.33,0:02:51.04,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,还有一种方法是在银幕上加上隐藏的圆点图案，每个影院的图案都不同
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.33,0:02:51.04,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,There's also hidden patterns of dots on the screens that differ from theatre to theatre,
Dialogue: 2,0:02:51.04,0:02:55.56,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这样通过观察这些圆点，就能知道某个枪版是从哪个电影院流出来的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.04,0:02:55.56,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,so that you'd be able to see which movie theatre a camcopy came from by looking at these dots.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:55.56,0:02:58.74,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这些圆点通常是看不见的，但如果你知道它们在哪以及如何找到它们
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.56,0:02:58.74,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,You wouldn't usually be able to see these, but if you knew where they were and how to find them,
Dialogue: 2,0:02:58.74,0:03:00.44,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,那你就能找到是哪家影院了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.74,0:03:00.44,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,then you'd be able to find the theatre.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:00.44,0:03:04.50,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,有些影院还配备了夜视技术，专门用来在黑暗中抓偷录的人
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.44,0:03:04.50,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Some theatres also have night vision technology to catch people recording in the dark.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:04.50,0:03:08.02,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,所以总结一下枪版，基本上就是有人在电影院里录电影
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.50,0:03:08.02,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,So camcopies, to sum it up, are basically someone recording the movie in the theatre
Dialogue: 2,0:03:08.02,0:03:12.22,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,还得把摄像机藏起来，结果就是画质烂得像坨翔，画面裁剪得乱七八糟
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.02,0:03:12.22,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,and hiding the camera which results in dogshit quality, poorly cropped footage,
Dialogue: 2,0:03:12.22,0:03:14.55,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,音质也差到爆，因为用的就是摄像机自带的麦克风
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.22,0:03:14.55,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,terrible audio since it's just using the camera's mic, 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:14.55,0:03:16.44,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,还有观众的噪音，甚至可能有人影晃动
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.55,0:03:16.44,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,audience noise, potential silhouette,
Dialogue: 2,0:03:16.44,0:03:18.70,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,总之，这不是看电影的好方式
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.44,0:03:18.70,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,and yeah, this isn't a good way to watch a movie.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:18.70,0:03:20.94,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,接下来，我们来看看TS版
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.70,0:03:20.94,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Moving on, we also have Telesync.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:20.94,0:03:22.80,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,你就是个海盗
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.94,0:03:22.80,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,You are a pirate!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:22.80,0:03:25.36,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,TS版的质量比枪版要好得多
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.80,0:03:25.36,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Telesyncs are much better quality than camcopies.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:25.36,0:03:28.80,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,首先，准枪版的音频是直接从声源录制的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.36,0:03:28.80,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,For starters, a Telesync is recorded with a direct connection to a sound source,
Dialogue: 2,0:03:28.80,0:03:31.64,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,也就是说音频不是通过影院里的麦克风录的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.80,0:03:31.64,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,meaning the audio isn't being recorded through a microphone in the theatre,
Dialogue: 2,0:03:31.64,0:03:35.36,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而是直接从源头录制，这样不仅音质更高
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.64,0:03:35.36,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,it's just being recorded straight from the source which won't just make it higher quality,
Dialogue: 2,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.10,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,还能消除任何观众的噪音
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.10,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,but will also get rid of any audience noise.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:37.10,0:03:41.00,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,TS版通常还会用更好的摄像机和三脚架
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.10,0:03:41.00,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Telesync are also usually recorded with a better camera on a tripod,
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.00,0:03:43.90,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而且是在放映室里录的，这意味着拍摄角度会更好
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.00,0:03:43.90,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,in the actual projection booth itself, meaning the angle will be better
Dialogue: 2,0:03:43.90,0:03:46.68,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,不会有糟糕的裁剪或者挡在前面的人影
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.90,0:03:46.68,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,and there won't be bad cropping or silhouette of people in the way,
Dialogue: 2,0:03:46.68,0:03:49.32,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但这也意味着很可能是影院员工干的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.68,0:03:49.32,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,but also means it will likely be done by an employee at the theatre,
Dialogue: 2,0:03:49.32,0:03:52.66,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,所以风险要大得多，因为一旦被抓，他们就会丢掉工作
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.32,0:03:52.66,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,so it's a much higher risk, because if they get caught, they'll lose their job,
Dialogue: 2,0:03:52.66,0:03:54.38,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这对他们未来的职业生涯可不是什么好事
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.66,0:03:54.38,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,and that won't be a great look for them in the future.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:54.38,0:03:58.46,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,摄像机的设置通常也会被调整，以每秒24帧的速度拍摄
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.38,0:03:58.46,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,The camera settings are also usually altered so that it shoots in 24 frames per second,
Dialogue: 2,0:03:58.46,0:04:01.50,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这样就和电影的帧率匹配了，曝光之类的参数也会调好
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.46,0:04:01.50,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,like how the film would be running, so they match, and the exposure on all the cameras,
Dialogue: 2,0:04:01.52,0:04:05.24,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,总之效果会更好，这里是枪版和TS版的对比
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.52,0:04:05.24,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,but that would be better. Here's a comparison between a cam and telesync.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:19.51,0:04:21.18,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,接下来是胶片转录版
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.51,0:04:21.18,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Now next up is a Telecine.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:21.18,0:04:25.14,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,想干嘛就干嘛，海盗的生活就是这么潇洒，你就是个海盗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.18,0:04:25.14,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Do what you want, that's a pirate that's free! You are a pirate!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:25.14,0:04:29.64,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这基本上就是有人用这种胶片转录机来复制电影胶片
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.14,0:04:29.64,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Which is essentially when someone makes a copy of the actual film using one of these telesyn machines.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:29.64,0:04:33.90,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这种是质量最好的版本，基本上和你买的DVD没啥区别
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.64,0:04:33.90,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,These are like, the best quality ones, and are basically the same as what you'd see on a DVD,
Dialogue: 2,0:04:33.90,0:04:36.02,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,因为它本质上就是对电影胶片的直接拷贝
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.90,0:04:36.02,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,since it is basically just a copy of the actual film.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:36.02,0:04:40.28,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,然而，这种版本极其罕见，因为要制作胶片转录版
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.02,0:04:40.28,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,However, these are incredibly rare, due to the fact that to actually get a Telecine copy,
Dialogue: 2,0:04:40.28,0:04:44.36,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,盗版贩子需要搞到一份电影胶片，还有一台胶片转录机
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.28,0:04:44.36,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,the bootleggers would need a copy of the film, and also a Telecine machine,
Dialogue: 2,0:04:44.36,0:04:47.24,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,说实话，这两样东西都挺难弄到手的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.36,0:04:47.24,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,which, I mean, both those things are quite hard to come by.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:47.24,0:04:49.50,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,所以大多数时候，盗版贩子会选择其他方式
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.24,0:04:49.50,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And so most of the time, bootleggers opt for one of the other options.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:49.50,0:04:53.04,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,还有一种叫“工作样片”，就是电影的未完成草稿版
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.50,0:04:53.04,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,There's also work prints, which is like, a rough unfinished version of the film,
Dialogue: 2,0:04:53.04,0:04:55.74,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,通常屏幕上会有时间码和水印之类的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.04,0:04:55.74,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,generally with stuff like times and watermarks on the screen.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:55.74,0:04:58.92,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,你们知道吗，那部还没上映的痞老板大电影，整个都在推特上泄露了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.74,0:04:58.92,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,You know how the entire Plankton movie that's not out yet leaked on Twitter?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:58.92,0:05:02.18,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,对，那就是工作样片，我一帧画面都不会给你们看的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.92,0:05:02.18,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's a work print, and I'm not gonna show a single frame,
Dialogue: 2,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.08,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,因为维亚康姆（Viacom）肯定会把我的频道给炸了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.08,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,because Viacom would absolutely nuke my channel.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:04.08,0:05:06.98,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这种泄露极其罕见，不常发生
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.08,0:05:06.98,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,These are ultra shiny rare, and don't happen often.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:06.98,0:05:09.76,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,不过连续两部海绵宝宝电影在上映前都发生了这种事
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.98,0:05:09.76,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Happened to two Spongebob movies in a row before they came out though.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:09.76,0:05:12.29,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,另外，据说《鼠国流浪记》有一个早期版本
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.76,0:05:12.29,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Also, supposedly, there's an early version of Flushed Away,
Dialogue: 2,0:05:12.29,0:05:15.16,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,里面有两个被从正片中剪掉的老鼠管家角色
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.29,0:05:15.16,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,featuring two Rat Butler guys that are cut from the film,
Dialogue: 2,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.94,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这个版本曾以《鼠国流浪记2》的名义在盗版DVD上发行
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.94,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,which was released on bootleg DVDs as Flushed Away 2.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:17.94,0:05:20.86,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,只是想提一下，虽然这个版本现在已经失传了，但还是挺有意思的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.94,0:05:20.86,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Just wanted to mention that, I mean, it is lost right now, but still.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:20.86,0:05:23.64,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,现在我们来说说直接从DVD翻录的版本
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.86,0:05:23.64,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Now we get to straight up rips of DVDs.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:23.64,0:05:27.36,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,比如我手上这张《人生遥控器》，它和正版的没任何区别
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.64,0:05:27.36,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Like, I have one of Click, and it's just the same as a normal Click DVD.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:27.36,0:05:28.46,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,哦，是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.36,0:05:28.46,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Hmm, oh really?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:28.46,0:05:30.98,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这些和正版DVD一模一样，但价格会更便宜
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.46,0:05:30.98,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,These are just the same as normal DVDs, but they'd be cheaper.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:30.98,0:05:32.04,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,不过现在这都不重要了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.98,0:05:32.04,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:32.04,0:05:34.92,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,看来我只能把这张盘加到我那堆积如山的《人生遥控器》DVD收藏里了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.04,0:05:34.92,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Guess I'll just add this Click to the ever-growing pile of Click DVDs.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:34.92,0:05:36.92,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,好了，盗版DVD的种类就介绍到这里
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.92,0:05:36.92,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Anyway, that covers the types of bootleg DVDs.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:36.92,0:05:40.32,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,现在，我觉得聊聊盗版贩子被抓的案例会很有趣
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.92,0:05:40.32,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Now, I thought it'd be interesting to go over instances where bootleggers were caught.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:40.32,0:05:46.08,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,首先来看一个来自底特律WXYZ-TV第七频道的视频
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.32,0:05:46.08,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Starting off with a video from WXYZ-TV Detroit Channel 7,
Dialogue: 2,0:05:46.08,0:05:46.59,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,标题是
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.08,0:05:46.59,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,titled,
Dialogue: 2,0:05:46.59,0:05:48.68,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,《盗版贩子在本地电影院被抓》
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.59,0:05:48.68,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Bootleggers Caught at a Local Movie Theater.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:48.68,0:05:50.64,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这是一则新闻报道，内容嘛，就是
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.68,0:05:50.64,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Which is a news report about, well,
Dialogue: 2,0:05:50.64,0:05:52.82,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,盗版贩子在本地电影院被抓了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.64,0:05:52.82,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,bootleggers being caught at a local movie theater.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:52.82,0:05:55.82,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这件事发生在密歇根州克林顿镇的一家星光影院
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.82,0:05:55.82,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,So this happened at a Star Theater in Clinton Township, Michigan,
Dialogue: 2,0:05:55.82,0:05:57.88,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,当时有两个家伙试图偷录一部电影
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.82,0:05:57.88,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,where there were two guys trying to film a movie.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:57.88,0:06:01.74,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他们当场被抓，这让我们能清楚地看到他们的作案工具
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.88,0:06:01.74,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,They were caught while doing it, and this gives us a pretty good look at their setup here.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:01.74,0:06:03.36,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他们用的是一台索尼摄像机
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.74,0:06:03.36,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,They were using a Sony camcorder.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:03.36,0:06:06.52,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,我不是什么摄像机专家，但据我判断
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.36,0:06:06.52,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Now, I'm no camera expert, but from what I can tell,
Dialogue: 2,0:06:06.52,0:06:12.21,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,看起来像是这款，索尼HDR-CX430V
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.52,0:06:12.21,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,it appears to be this camera, the Sony HDR-CX430V
Dialogue: 2,0:06:12.21,0:06:15.48,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,高清闪存手持摄像机
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.21,0:06:15.48,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,High Definition Flash Memory Handycam Camcorder,
Dialogue: 2,0:06:15.48,0:06:17.30,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这款摄像机是在2013年1月发布的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.48,0:06:17.30,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,which was released back in January 2013,
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.30,0:06:20.74,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,so it makes sense with this news report being released in October 2013.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:17.34,0:06:20.74,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而这则新闻报道是2013年10月的，所以时间上对得上
Dialogue: 2,0:06:20.74,0:06:22.20,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,不过要是有说错的，欢迎指正
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.74,0:06:22.20,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But feel free to correct me.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:22.20,0:06:27.26,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,总之，他们用这个夹子把摄像机固定在影院座位的扶手上
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.20,0:06:27.26,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Anyway, they had this clamp here that they used to attach it onto the armrest of the theater seats.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:27.26,0:06:30.64,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,固定好之后，他们用一条毛巾盖住，以免被发现
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.26,0:06:30.64,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Once that was set up, they covered it with a towel so they couldn't get caught.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.42,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,虽然最后还是被抓了，但想法是好的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.42,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,I mean, it didn't work, but still.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:32.42,0:06:36.02,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他们当时试图偷录的电影是2013年的《地心引力》
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.42,0:06:36.02,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,The specific movie they were attempting to film was the 2013 movie Gravity.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:36.02,0:06:39.50,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这两个家伙之所以被抓，多亏了我们前面提到的隐藏水印
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.02,0:06:39.50,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Now, the way these fellas got caught was thanks to the previously mentioned hidden watermarks
Dialogue: 2,0:06:39.50,0:06:43.21,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,通过这些水印，人们追踪到了他们之前一些盗版电影的确切拍摄影院
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.50,0:06:43.21,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,that were used to track down the exact theater that some of their previous bootlegs were filmed at.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:43.21,0:06:46.73,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,于是，一名私家侦探被派往该影院，并成功抓住了他们
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.21,0:06:46.73,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,So, a private investigator was sent to the theater and was able to catch them.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:46.73,0:06:49.64,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,我没查到这两个人最后到底怎么样了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.73,0:06:49.64,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Now, I can't find what ended up happening to these specific guys,
Dialogue: 2,0:06:49.64,0:06:52.96,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但新闻报道确实给了我们一些线索，让我们能猜到他们的下场
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.64,0:06:52.96,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,but the news report does give us a little insight as to what might have happened.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:52.96,0:06:53.44,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.96,0:06:53.44,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Boom!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:53.44,0:06:57.20,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,初犯的话，要罚款一万美元，外加一年监禁
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.44,0:06:57.20,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,So for a first offence, it'd be a $10,000 fine and one year in jail.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:57.20,0:06:59.86,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,再犯的话罚金和刑期翻倍，三进宫的话再翻倍
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.20,0:06:59.86,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Then it doubles for second offence and dubs again for third offence.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:59.86,0:07:00.86,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,所以，下场不咋地
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.86,0:07:00.86,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,So, not great.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:00.86,0:07:02.97,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,不管怎样，这两个家伙是把电影传到网上的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.86,0:07:02.97,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Anyway, these guys were posting these movies online.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:02.97,0:07:05.78,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,那么，我们来看看卖盗版DVD的案例怎么样
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.97,0:07:05.78,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,So, how about we look at someone selling bootleg DVDs?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:05.78,0:07:06.92,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,想干嘛就干嘛，因为海盗是自由的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.78,0:07:06.92,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Do what you want, cause the pirate is free!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:06.92,0:07:11.04,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这件事发生在2011年的佛罗里达州波尔克县
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.92,0:07:11.04,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,This event took place in 2011 and happened in Polk County, Florida.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:11.04,0:07:14.94,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这背后涉及一个完整的犯罪团伙，警方查获了八千张盗版DVD
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.04,0:07:14.94,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,There was a whole crime ring involved here and 8,000 bootleg DVDs were found.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:14.94,0:07:18.26,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,我们能看到一些照片，让我们得以一窥他们幕后的操作
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.94,0:07:18.26,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,We get to see some photos that give us a behind the scenes look at the operation here.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:18.26,0:07:24.17,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,第一张图只是一堆盗版DVD，据说当时售价是正版DVD的一半
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.26,0:07:24.17,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Our first image simply shows a stack of bootleg DVDs that were apparently being sold for half the price of regular DVDs at the time.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:24.17,0:07:29.26,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,第二张图显示了他们成堆的同款电影，所以我们能看到他们当时在卖些什么
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.17,0:07:29.26,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Our second image shows there's stacks of the same movie, so we can see some of the stuff they were selling.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:29.26,0:07:32.74,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这里有《里约大冒险》，这里是《绿灯侠》，那边还有《惊声尖叫》等等
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.26,0:07:32.74,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,We have Rio here, Green Lantern here, Scream there and many more.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:32.74,0:07:36.15,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,我们还有一张最有趣的图片，由于某种原因，感觉像是那个
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.74,0:07:36.15,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,We also have the most interesting image, which for some reason seems to be taken 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:36.15,0:07:39.22,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在网上爆料《任天堂明星大乱斗》的哥们儿拍的，因为实在是太糊了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.15,0:07:39.22,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,by the same guy who posted Smash Bros. leaks online because it's really blurry.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:39.22,0:07:42.42,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但我们还是能看到这边堆着一摞摞的电影盒和封套
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.22,0:07:42.42,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But we can actually see stacks of cases and sleeves for movies over here 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:42.42,0:07:46.30,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,还有那边一大堆准备刻录的空白DVD
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.42,0:07:46.30,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,along with a shit ton of blank DVDs ready to have movies burnt to them over here.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:46.30,0:07:49.17,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而且，这些家伙以每张大约一美元的价格买入这些DVD
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.30,0:07:49.17,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Also, these guys were buying these DVDs for like a dollar each 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:49.17,0:07:51.54,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,然后在亚马逊和eBay上当正品卖
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.17,0:07:51.54,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,and selling them on Amazon and eBay as legit.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:51.54,0:07:55.18,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,从而赚取了巨额利润，每周高达两万美金，哎我曹乐
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.54,0:07:55.18,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Thus making a load of money, up to 20 grand a week, god damn.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:55.18,0:07:57.70,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他们总共从中获利五十万美元
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.18,0:07:57.70,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,They in total made half a million dollars from this.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:57.70,0:08:01.68,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,现在，如果我告诉你盗版DVD其实还没死透，你会怎么想
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.70,0:08:01.68,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Now, what if I told you that bootleg DVDs aren't actually a dead thing?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:01.68,0:08:03.84,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,你可能会惊讶，但也可能不会
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.68,0:08:03.84,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,You might be surprised, but also maybe not.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:03.84,0:08:05.30,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,如今的情况有点不同
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.84,0:08:05.30,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,It's a little different nowadays 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:05.30,0:08:10.55,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,很多盗版只是发行一些从未有过DVD版本的东西，还有一些是VHS录像带的转录
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.30,0:08:10.55,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,with lots of them just being releases of things that never actually had DVD releases and also some of VHS releases.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:10.55,0:08:14.46,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但大多数时候，买这些东西的人完全知道它们不是正品
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.55,0:08:14.46,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But most of the time people buying these are fully aware they're not real.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:14.46,0:08:17.75,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,更多的是他们只是想拥有这些东西的实体版而已
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.46,0:08:17.75,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,It's more that they just want to own a physical version of some of these.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:17.75,0:08:20.17,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,就好像，没人会买一盘《地狱客栈》的录像带
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.75,0:08:20.17,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Like, no one is buying a has-been-hotel VHS 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:20.17,0:08:22.50,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,还以为这是亚马逊百分百官方正品吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.17,0:08:22.50,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,thinking it's a 100% official Amazon product.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:22.50,0:08:25.15,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但有时候盗版DVD还是会被当成正品来卖
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.50,0:08:25.15,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But sometimes bootleg DVDs are sold as legitimate, 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:25.15,0:08:27.46,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,就像我在一个视频里看到的这些《开心汉堡店》的DVD
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.15,0:08:27.46,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,like these Bob's Berkus DVDs I saw in a video.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:27.46,0:08:29.94,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,不过比起当年，现在这个问题已经小很多了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.46,0:08:29.94,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,It's still a much smaller problem than it was back then though.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:29.94,0:08:32.64,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,总之，感谢推特账号“Theater Bootleg Archives”
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.94,0:08:32.64,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Anyway, thanks to the Twitter account Theater Bootleg Archives, 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:32.64,0:08:34.84,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他们也有个油管频道，你应该去订阅一下
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.64,0:08:34.84,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,they also have a YouTube channel you should sub to.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:34.84,0:08:39.44,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这个视频很棒，我们关于盗版DVD世界的探险也差不多该结束了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.84,0:08:39.44,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,This video is great, and that about wraps up our adventure into the world of bootleg DVDs.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:39.48,0:08:42.84,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,了解了背后的故事后，看看这些东西还挺有意思的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.48,0:08:42.84,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,These things are cool to look at knowing the story behind them, but 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:42.84,0:08:45.48,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但随着互联网的普及，这门手艺已经几近失传
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.84,0:08:45.48,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,they're an almost dead art at this point with the internet existing.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:45.48,0:08:49.19,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,用这种方式看电影体验极差，我想没人会喜欢看这种东西，但是
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.48,0:08:49.19,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,They're a terrible way to watch a movie, I don't think anyone enjoys watching these, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:49.19,0:08:54.17,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,如果你想在《龙凤双胞》还在影院上映时就在家看，那你也只能将就了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.19,0:08:54.17,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,If you wanted to watch Jack and Jill at home before it finished its theatrical run, you'd have to settle.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:54.58,0:08:55.64,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,另外，你为啥要看那玩意儿，你有毛病吗
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.58,0:08:55.64,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Also, why? What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:55.64,0:08:57.20,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,总之，快去看《沙雕校园》
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.64,0:08:57.20,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Anyway, watch our stupid school. 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:57.20,0:09:00.04,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这是我制作的节目，我也在里面，看，这是它的枪版
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.20,0:09:00.04,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,It's a show I made, and I'm in. Look, here's a cam copy of it.